[This report eliminates the possibility that this was a case of urban
acquired yellow fever virus infection (ProMED-mail archive no. 20081231.4119).

A map of the border area where Paraguay, Argentina and Brazil join, showing
Misiones province, where the infection was presumably acquired, can be
accessed at <http://www.lib.utexas.edu/maps/americas/argentina_pol96.jpg>.
The HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of Argentina is available at
<http://healthmap.org/promed/en?g=3429886&v=-30.4,-64.2,5>. - Mod.TY]
